OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBorder staff at airports to
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstrike over Christmas      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Border Force staff are going on strike 
OL,6, for eight days over Christmas at       
OL,7, Heathrow, Gatwick and several other    
OL,8, airports, the PCS union has announced. 
OL,10,FAbout 75% of passport control staff are
OL,11,FPCS members - and Heathrow has warned  
OL,12,Fchecks may take longer on strike days. 
OL,14,FThousands of other civil servants -    
OL,15,Fincluding driving test examiners - will
OL,16,Falso be taking industrial action.      
OL,18,FPCS boss Mark Serwotka said the strikes
OL,19,Fwould "escalate" unless the government 
OL,20,F"put money on the table now".          
